  [惰性区], [`theta_1 <= SF <= theta_2`], [`R(SF) = 0`],
  [成骨区], [`theta_2 < SF <= theta_f`], [`R(SF) = c_2 (SF - (theta_2 + theta_f)/2)^2 + alpha r_sat`],
